      "num": 2,
      "text": "A private examiner interviews an employee about policy violations. The employee is not in police custody. Which right is the examiner NOT legally obligated to provide?",
      "tag": "Rights of the Investigated",
      "options": [
        "A. Miranda Warnings (right to remain silent and right to counsel)",
        "B. Notification that the interview is voluntary",
        "C. Opportunity to present their version of the facts",
        "D. Access to the final investigation report"
